      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "Think of something difficult you went through that you're no longer in. An illness you recovered from. A painful situation that resolved. A dark period that eventually lifted. You survived it. You're here. That difficulty is behind you now. Can you feel grateful for that?"\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "grat_013"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Someone's Smile"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "category"\cf12 : \cf14 "people"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "duration_seconds"\cf12 : \cf15 60\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "difficulty"\cf12 : \cf14 "beginner"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "tags"\cf12 : \cf11 [\cf14 "connection"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "kindness"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "human"\cf11 ],\cf12 \
      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "Recall a time someone smiled at you genuinely. Maybe today, maybe recently. A smile is a gift of warmth and recognition. Someone saw you and responded with openness. That moment of human connection, however brief, mattered. Can you appreciate it now?"\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "grat_014"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Your Strengths"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "category"\cf12 : \cf14 "self"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "duration_seconds"\cf12 : \cf15 90\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "difficulty"\cf12 : \cf14 "intermediate"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
