      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "What season of life are you in? Spring with new beginnings? Summer with full bloom and activity? Autumn with release and letting go? Winter with rest and restoration? Each season has its purpose. You can't force spring in winter. Can you accept the season you're in and honor what it requires? The seasons always change. This one will too."\cf12 \
