      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "My breath is my anchor. It's always here, always available. When I feel lost or overwhelmed, I can return to my breath. One breath at a time. One moment at a time. My breath reminds me that I'm alive, I'm here, I'm okay."\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
