      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "I am enough, exactly as I am. Not when I accomplish more. Not when I change. Right now. I am enough. My worth is not conditional. I don't have to earn my place here. I belong. I am enough."\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "aff_004"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Presence Choice"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "category"\cf12 : \cf14 "agency"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "duration_seconds"\cf12 : \cf15 60\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "difficulty"\cf12 : \cf14 "beginner"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "tags"\cf12 : \cf11 [\cf14 "presence"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "choice"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "now"\cf11 ],\cf12 \
      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "I choose to be present. The past is gone. The future hasn't arrived. This moment is all there is, and I choose to be here for it. Fully. Completely. I choose presence over distraction. I choose now."\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "aff_005"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Self-Compassion"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "category"\cf12 : \cf14 "kindness"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "duration_seconds"\cf12 : \cf15 75\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "difficulty"\cf12 : \cf14 "beginner"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "tags"\cf12 : \cf11 [\cf14 "compassion"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "kindness"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "self_care"\cf11 ],\cf12 \
      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "I offer myself compassion. I'm doing the best I can with what I have. My struggles are real. My pain matters. I deserve the same kindness I'd give to someone I love. I am worthy of my own care and compassion."\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "aff_006"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Release and Flow"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "category"\cf12 : \cf14 "letting_go"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "duration_seconds"\cf12 : \cf15 75\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "difficulty"\cf12 : \cf14 "intermediate"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "tags"\cf12 : \cf11 [\cf14 "release"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "flow"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "surrender"\cf11 ],\cf12 \
      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "I release what I cannot control. I let go of my grip on outcomes. I trust the flow of life. Not everything requires my effort. Not everything needs to be fixed. I can soften. I can allow. I can flow."\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "aff_007"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Body Acceptance"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "category"\cf12 : \cf14 "acceptance"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "duration_seconds"\cf12 : \cf15 75\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "difficulty"\cf12 : \cf14 "intermediate"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "tags"\cf12 : \cf11 [\cf14 "body"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "acceptance"\cf11 ,\cf12  \cf14 "gratitude"\cf11 ],\cf12 \
      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "I accept my body as it is. It's been with me through everything. It works for me every day, even when I criticize it. I choose to treat my body with respect and care. This body is my home. I am grateful for it."\cf12 \
    \cf11 \},\cf12 \
    \cf11 \{\cf12 \
      \cf13 "id"\cf12 : \cf14 "aff_008"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
      \cf13 "name"\cf12 : \cf14 "Permission to Feel"\cf11 ,\cf12 \
