      \cf13 "text"\cf12 : \cf14 "I acknowledge my fear. I don't have to pretend it's not there. Fear is information. It's trying to protect me. I can feel afraid and still move forward. Courage isn't the absence of fear. It's action in the presence of fear. I am brave."\cf12 \
